  "description": [
    "D C Womens Match Play Enters SemiFinal Round Mrs Tucker Mrs Amick Top Golf COLUMBIA SITE Taking Mrs charlotte Stern of Indian Spring into camp by the lopsided count of 6 and 5 in the quarterfinal play of the Womens District Golf Association match play tournament for the Post Cup at Columbia Country Club yester day afternoon Mrs A W Tucker of Beaver Dam Country Club es tablished herself as an outside choice to get by Mrs Earl Amick of Columbia today to go into the finals tomorrow Mrs Betty Meckley of Indian Spring eliminated Mrs Arnold McNitt of Congressional yester day 4 and 3 and will meet Marian Brown the George Washington coed advanced by defeating Mrs J H Bullock of Indian Spring 2 and 1 Mrs Meckley is highly frvored over the Manor collegian John McClure won the Presi dents Cup as 65 members of the National Press Club staged their sixth annual tournament over Kenwood Club yesterday as he scored a low gross of 72 two over par Second low gross was captured by E A Merkle who posted an 83 Low net winners included L Roy 912071 Frank Buck ONeill 871572 W J McEvoy 851273 C"
